Author: Rivka90
Text: I've lost and regained 20lbs between Sept 17 and Oct 14. I feel this so hard.

Author: OverGi
Text: Lmao, im going to make you feel better and tell u what I did: so I reached my lowest weight like *ever* (but not goal weight yet) and then for some reason decided that I was skinny enough and I could eat a lot now (a ridiculous amount, honestly) and nothing would happen, so I did just that and fast forward 3 months and SURPRISE im the heaviest i have *ever* been. And the thing is i wasnt even mad, i was like "*what* on earth did i do that for?" and i could only facepalm myself. lmao. So now im starting all over again tsk tsk
